35:30.080 --> 35:32.162
Everything
is "copastetic."

35:32.210 --> 35:35.168
- Okay.
- We're wonderful.
Everything's wonderful.

35:35.220 --> 35:38.303
- How are you, Holleood?
- I missed you.
How's my baby Blue?

35:38.350 --> 35:39.999
- He good.
- Yeah?

35:40.050 --> 35:43.395
Everybody's getting
some hugs up in here today.

35:43.440 --> 35:46.091
[ all chattering ]

35:46.140 --> 35:48.005
We got something
to celebrate!
Come on!

35:48.050 --> 35:50.132
[ music playing ]

35:50.190 --> 35:52.658
[ laughter]

35:52.710 --> 35:54.792
He wasn't doing none of that
before I got there.

35:54.840 --> 35:56.182
I sure wasn't.

35:56.240 --> 35:58.049
I got it now, though!
Unh!

35:58.110 --> 36:00.840
[ laughter]

36:00.890 --> 36:03.108
Violet:
You dope.

36:04.240 --> 36:06.982
[ laughter continues ]

36:16.210 --> 36:18.166
- [ water running ]
- [ dishes clanking ]

36:21.480 --> 36:23.562
Oh, baby, I got it.
You don't have to do that.

36:23.610 --> 36:25.862
No, no,
it's your special night.

36:25.920 --> 36:28.957
I got it.

36:29.010 --> 36:32.264
Well, now everybody knows
that you hate to clean.

36:32.320 --> 36:35.005
Been that way
since you were a girl.

36:35.060 --> 36:39.178
Yes, but even I know
that taking care

36:39.240 --> 36:41.185
of the things
and the people
that you love

36:41.240 --> 36:43.105
is what makes
a house a home.

36:45.890 --> 36:48.154
I miss that feeling.

36:49.330 --> 36:51.764
Well, ain't nothing
to miss.

36:51.810 --> 36:54.244
You're home,
long as you want it.

36:59.600 --> 37:01.818
[ chattering ]

37:04.650 --> 37:07.175
- [ distant dog barking ]
- [ distant train horn
blaring ]

37:26.850 --> 37:28.977
- What's up?
- What's going on?

37:32.510 --> 37:33.670
Hey...

37:38.290 --> 37:39.689
you gonna be okay?

37:42.080 --> 37:43.513
I think so.

37:45.130 --> 37:47.291
Keep your head up.

37:47.350 --> 37:48.510
You hear me?

37:51.920 --> 37:53.603
Gonna be fine.

37:54.750 --> 37:56.138
We'll see y'all.

38:04.100 --> 38:05.442
Thank you for that.

38:08.320 --> 38:10.231
Ain't nothing.

38:10.280 --> 38:11.884
I want you know
I get it.

38:14.460 --> 38:17.543
You need to stand
on your own.

38:17.590 --> 38:20.150
Daddy left you
part of the land, and...

38:20.210 --> 38:24.249
you should be able to do
with it what others do.

38:24.300 --> 38:27.940
Leverage it.
Build credibility.

38:28.000 --> 38:30.992
Use it to get ahead.

38:32.960 --> 38:35.121
I'll sign the papers
for the microloan.

38:44.140 --> 38:45.482
Thank you.

38:47.490 --> 38:50.755
[ indistinct chatter ]

38:50.800 --> 38:53.325
Oh, wh--
where are you all going?

38:53.370 --> 38:54.758
You and Micah
don't have to go nowhere.

38:54.810 --> 38:56.368
Yes, we do.

38:56.420 --> 38:58.581
You and Hollywood
have been apart for a while.

38:58.640 --> 39:00.369
We're gonna
get out of here

39:00.420 --> 39:02.069
because no one wants
to hear all that.

39:02.120 --> 39:04.372
No, no, no.
I-- I won't have it.

39:04.420 --> 39:06.593
- You don't have to--
- No, she got a point.

39:06.640 --> 39:08.460
Grown folks gotta be grown.

39:10.600 --> 39:12.477
And now that you're back,
I think it's time

39:12.520 --> 39:14.772
I start looking
for a place, too.

39:14.830 --> 39:16.343
Baby, you don't
have to do that.

39:19.480 --> 39:21.744
See you lovebirds
in a couple days.

39:21.790 --> 39:23.178
Bye.

39:23.230 --> 39:25.744
- Love you, Micah.
- Love you, too.

39:25.790 --> 39:28.918
- Love you, Vi.
- Love you, Hollywood.

39:28.970 --> 39:31.359
Mmm...

39:35.320 --> 39:37.800
Hey.
How are you?

39:37.850 --> 39:38.885
Fine.

39:42.850 --> 39:44.670
I'm gonna be
in my room.

39:58.300 --> 40:00.439
I'm surprised
you brought him back.

40:00.480 --> 40:04.439
You said you want a chance
to be a father to our son.

40:04.480 --> 40:05.959
And I don't like it.

40:07.970 --> 40:10.746
But we'll share him
because I think he needs it.

40:12.710 --> 40:13.961
Maybe you do, too.

40:18.590 --> 40:20.455
You know, I would have
never called the bank

40:20.500 --> 40:22.320
about your mill loan,
Charley.

40:22.370 --> 40:24.622
I know that you did
what you've always done,

40:24.680 --> 40:27.854
and that's whatever
you had to do, so.

40:27.900 --> 40:29.856
I got word
the loan funds
tomorrow,

40:29.900 --> 40:33.074
so... thank you.

40:34.470 --> 40:36.290
But you should know...

40:36.340 --> 40:39.810
if you mess this up,
I will find a way to end it.

40:41.430 --> 40:43.819
I will do right
by our son.

40:43.870 --> 40:46.088
I hope so, Davis.

40:48.920 --> 40:50.228
I hope so.

40:57.320 --> 40:58.799
- Checking out.
- Okay.

40:58.840 --> 41:00.239
Room 716.

41:02.280 --> 41:03.838
- Here.
- Thank you.

41:14.080 --> 41:15.593
Well, hello there.

41:15.640 --> 41:17.949
Good morning.
Coffee?

41:17.990 --> 41:20.163
You just happen
to have two?

41:20.210 --> 41:22.201
Well, you know,

41:22.260 --> 41:23.818
I took up
a lot of your time
yesterday.

41:23.870 --> 41:27.340
I-- felt only right
that I give you
a proper sendoff.

41:27.390 --> 41:30.518
Thank you, Dr. Dubois,
for our walk

41:30.570 --> 41:32.526
and especially
for our conversation.

41:32.570 --> 41:34.390
I enjoyed it.

41:34.440 --> 41:36.044
Likewise.

41:36.100 --> 41:39.479
If you ever get
away from Atlanta
and make your way

41:39.540 --> 41:42.316
to New Orleans,
I'll have to return the favor.

41:44.240 --> 41:46.185
Okay. All right.
May I?

41:46.240 --> 41:47.628
- Yes.
- All right.

41:54.810 --> 41:56.937
Listen...

41:56.990 --> 41:59.720
I could take you
to the airport
if you'd like.

41:59.770 --> 42:02.512
I'm okay, thank you.

42:02.560 --> 42:04.073
All right.

42:04.130 --> 42:08.294
Um, if you ever need
some epidemiological...

42:08.350 --> 42:09.772
[laughs]

42:09.830 --> 42:12.435
No, no, seriously,
expertise, I just...

42:12.480 --> 42:14.209
You'll be
my ﬁrst call.

42:14.270 --> 42:16.784
Yes, ma'am.
I look forward
to that call, Queen.

42:19.010 --> 42:20.568
- Travel safe.
- Yeah.

42:20.620 --> 42:23.180
- Okay, all right.
- Thank you.

42:23.230 --> 42:24.447
...overhead,
swift courage

42:24.490 --> 42:29.439
Shoot it down, down

42:29.500 --> 42:33.459
Fill the lung that loves
the phosphorescent

42:33.500 --> 42:38.722
Absorbent time
spent on few

42:38.770 --> 42:40.590
And all of you

42:40.640 --> 42:43.461
I'll offer myrrh
and murder

42:43.510 --> 42:49.335
The preferred method
of doubt that sways about.
